title: Digital Puppet Masters Tournament Series 2 - 1v1 (Tonight 6.30pm AEDT)

embed.description: This organization will run tournaments for teams and players of all ranks and skill level, with a main focus on League Of Legends in the Oceanic Region.

body:
This tournament is a single elimination 1v1 event.
It will be first to take the Nexus on the Howling Abyss Map.

This is week 9 of the series.
Previous winners were Kayle {{champion:10}} , Nasus {{champion:75}} , Yorick {{champion:83}} , Jax {{champion:24}} , Trundle {{champion:48}} , Teemo {{champion:17}} , Darius {{champion:122}} and Tahm Kench {{champion:223}}  so are banned for the rest of the series. Who will be next.

If you are interested in playing register here --> https://battlefy.com/digital-puppet-masters 
for all other communication go here --> https://discord.gg/9RZRQhf 

Check-in will be between 6pm-6.30pm AEDT, the tournament will start at 6.30pm.
Note:- 6.30pm AEDT(NSW, ACT, Melbourne, Hobart) is equal to 5.30pm(Brisbane), 8.30pm (NZ), 6pm (SA), 3.30pm(WA), 5pm (NT)

Prizes are as follows :-
1st $10 Riot Gift Card

Riot has also allocated :-
1st Place: 750 RP
4-win XP boost for all participants

Regards Dungeon
